query:
UPDATE 
                gcp_trigger 
            SET 
                gcp_resource_path = $1,
                subscription_id = $2,
                topic_id = $3,
                delivery_type = $4,
                delivery_config = $5,
                is_flow = $6, 
                edited_by = $7, 
                email = $8,
                script_path = $9,
                path = $10,
                enabled = $11,
                edited_at = now(), 
                error = NULL,
                server_id = NULL,
                error_handler_path = $14,
                error_handler_args = $15,
                retry = $16,
                auto_acknowledge_msg = $17
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $12 AND 
                path = $13
